    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Adult individuals of Adelophryne glandulata sp. nov. in life: (A) male paratype (MZUESC 12180 — 10.2 mm), and (B) female paratype with eggs visible through flank skin (MNRJ 87080 — 12.8 mm)." ;
